#   Co-authored-by: Pat Smith <pat@example.com>
#
# ============================================================================
# VALIDATION RULES
# ============================================================================
#
# The commit-msg hook will validate:
#   ✓ Type is valid and present
#   ✓ Subject is present and ≤ 50 characters
#   ✓ Subject uses lowercase first letter
#   ✓ Subject has no trailing period
#   ✓ Scope is valid (if provided)
#   ✓ BREAKING CHANGE footer present when using "!"
#   ⚠ Context files are referenced if changed
#   ⚠ Body lines wrap at 72 characters
#
# To bypass validation (not recommended):
#   git commit --no-verify
#
# To configure validation level:
#   git config xeyth.commitValidation [strict|warn|disable]
#
# ============================================================================
